{"tid":1605955,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國議員質問外相：你最近就香港警隊做過啲咩外交交涉呢?","createTime":"2019-09-30T12:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T20:20:08.000Z","uid":305299,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"08b4d0091951b2e6cb0dec55593cd33912354667","tid":1605955,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KC9kMAh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKC9kMAh.jpg&h=00aeb812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國<del>一向出名廢嘅</del>工黨就香港議題最近好似有少少改咗作風，勇武咗啲啲咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係工黨預期保守黨政府好快會倒台要準備大選??? <br />\n<br />\n唔理咩原因，英國工黨議員Emily Thornberry 原來前幾日向政府提出書面質詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要知道上面依位工黨議員同時係影子外相，亦即係如果工黨突然上台，佢就有機會做下一任外交大臣(但唔一定嘅)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然英國現任外交大臣保守黨嘅藍韜文仲未回覆，<del>又今日突然話會考慮遲下推動立法制裁侵害人權人士，唔知同被人質問得多有無關</del>，但工黨議員質詢內容係：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>想請問外交大臣，佢最近向相對應嘅香港部門，對香港警隊就佢地國家近日示威活動嘅處理手法上，提出過咩外交交涉呢</blockquote><br />\n有幾點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一點，書面質詢其實唔係直接交畀政府大臣，而係首先交畀國會秘書處一個辦公室(Table Office)，所以個問題用嘅字眼係「佢」，而唔係「你」，但意思其實一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而依位議員點解用「國家」來形容香港呢? 話唔定佢想香港變成英國嘅組成國，好似Scotland咁?又話唔定佢暗底係香港勇武共和獨派? 當然依啲都係吹水，因為可能單純搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但重點係&hellip;</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地幫我地質問英國政府，我地好應該同人講多謝，而且順便畀多個理由佢繼續幫我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除咗用下面傳送門去佢嘅facebook 同 twitter 講多謝之外，仲要話佢知，我地會叫喺英國住嘅朋友同親戚考慮下次投票畀工黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然最後點投票無人知，但去留言嘅目的，就等同暗示只要佢繼續幫我地發聲，我地就會幫佢拉票，同時等於變相話畀其他英國政黨知，唔幫香港人係有壞處，就係選票流失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依度有個例子畀大家參考(<del>記得中學抄功課都識改用字</del>)：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Thank you for your recent written question to the Foreign Secretary about Hong Kong police brutality. Even I don&rsquo;t live in the UK, I&rsquo;ll still tell my friends and relatives now living in the UK about what you&rsquo;ve done for HK and ask them to consider voting for Labour in the next election. Go Labour Go!!! Or as we say it in HK, &ldquo;Add Oil~!&rdquo;<br />\n(多謝你最近畀外交大臣關於香港警察暴力嘅書面質詢。即使我唔係住喺英國，但我會同我喺英國住嘅親戚朋友講你之前為香港做過咩，同埋叫佢地考慮下次選舉個陣投票畀工黨。加油，工黨，加油!!!又或者我地香港嘅講法「加油~!」)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果英國政府官員唔想理我地，我地唔應該選擇灰心放棄，而係向國會議員埋手，因為美國戰線都係咁打來嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以BNO要登記做英國選民呀，無錯，BNO現身處係英國讀書工作生活都可以登記做英國選民，詳情下面有傳送門去教學 link<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋以後出來行，除左美國旗，仲要拎大量英國旗同香港旗，因為美國戰線都係一堆美國旗開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====質詢問題原文=====<br />\nTo ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, what recent representations he has made to his counterpart in Hong Kong on the conduct of the Hong Kong police force during recent demonstrations in that country.<br />\n=====傳送門：質詢問題=====<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.parliament.uk/business/publications/written-questions-answers-statements/written-question/Commons/2019-09-26/291321/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parliament.uk%2Fbusiness%2Fpublications%2Fwritten-questions-answers-statements%2Fwritten-question%2FCommons%2F2019-09-26%2F291321%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zt3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=8bd8b1c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.parliament.uk/business/publications/written-questions-answers-statements/written-question/Commons/2019-09-26/291321/</a><br />\n=====傳送門：英國工黨議員個facebook =====<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Emily-Thornberry-142202379163151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEmily-Thornberry-142202379163151&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zt3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=75b57ee9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Emily-Thornberry-142202379163151</a><br />\n=====傳送門：英國工黨議員個twitter =====<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/emilythornberry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Femilythornberry&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zt3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=bc433e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/emilythornberry</a><br />\n=====傳送門：BNO登記做英國選民=====<br />\n分享自 LIHKG 討論區: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595661</a><br />\n=====迷你歷史堂=====<br />\n1984-85年，英國保守黨戴卓爾夫人政府喺無公投情況下，同中國簽訂聯合聲明，並禁止BNO人獲得完整英國公民身份 (&lt;- 其實今年年頭，國際法庭指英國喺無公投下，喺65年將查戈斯群島從殖民地毛里裘斯分割出來嘅行為違反國際慣例法，亦即按道理所有英國殖民地嘅去留都應事先有公投，自然香港當年都應該要有公投)<br />\n<br />\n2008-09年，英國自民黨議員Lord Avebury喺國會堅持修改法例，擴大完整英國公民身份到非華裔又無其他國籍嘅BNO身上，最終迫使工黨白高敦政府同意咗，因此為97年後BNO逐步平權之路打開一個先例"},{"pid":"af31031453bfee5d6bafc6cd52ee6d22c1a02007","tid":1605955,"uid":94441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:22:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ef7a7b861430a252b7191bdddc4e3e825adf4f4","tid":1605955,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"推！好好去多謝人地啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf628a1ef08e1c05af636912db14b1a0787c4c3","tid":1605955,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:27:22.000Z","msg":"P仔好想推"},{"pid":"e0ea031545edaf6320fea065f2087f236e2f3df1","tid":1605955,"uid":228724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3afea354cb2d45db057a43bd4a7